\procedure presenterButtons()
<$button message="tm-mcp-claim-presenter" disabled=<<claimDisabled>>>Claim presenter</$button> <$button message="tm-mcp-release-presenter" disabled=<<releaseDisabled>>>Release presenter</$button>
\end

<$let
	mode={{{ [[$:/config/wikilabs/tw-mcp/mode]get[text]] :else[[default]] }}}
	mainCid={{{ [[$:/state/wikilabs/tw-mcp/main-clientId]get[text]] }}}
	mainName={{{ [[$:/state/wikilabs/tw-mcp/main-username]get[text]] }}}
	myCid={{{ [[$:/state/wikilabs/tw-mcp/my-clientId]get[text]] }}}
	presenterCid={{{ [[$:/state/wikilabs/tw-mcp/presenter-clientId]get[text]] }}}
	presenterName={{{ [[$:/state/wikilabs/tw-mcp/presenter-username]get[text]] }}}
	locked={{{ [<mode>!match[main]then[no]] :else[<mainCid>is[blank]then[no]] :else[<mainCid>match<myCid>then[no]else[yes]] }}}
	claimDisabled={{{ [<mode>!match[main]then[no]] :else[<mainCid>is[blank]then[no]else[yes]] }}}
	releaseDisabled={{{ [<mode>!match[main]then[no]] :else[<mainCid>is[blank]then[no]] :else[<mainCid>match<myCid>then[no]] :else[<presenterCid>match<myCid>then[no]else[yes]] }}}
>

! Broadcast mode

Controls how SSE events for ''per-tab view-state tiddlers'' (`$:/StoryList`, `$:/HistoryList`, `$:/state/*` by default) propagate between connected browser tabs. MCP-tool changes and filesystem-watcher edits always broadcast to all tabs, regardless of mode.

<% if [<locked>match[yes]] %>

//Settings are locked while another tab holds main. Current mode: ''<$text text=<<mode>>/>''.//

<% endif %>

<% if [<locked>match[no]] %>
<table>
<thead><tr><th></th><th>Mode</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr><td><$radio tiddler="$:/config/wikilabs/tw-mcp/mode" value="default" default="default"/></td><td>''Default''</td><td>Per-tab view state stays per-tab. Browser-originated `$:/StoryList` changes do not cross-sync.</td></tr>
<tr><td><$radio tiddler="$:/config/wikilabs/tw-mcp/mode" value="presentation"/></td><td>''Presentation''</td><td>One tab is the //presenter// and its view-state changes broadcast to all other tabs. Last-claim-wins.</td></tr>
<tr><td><$radio tiddler="$:/config/wikilabs/tw-mcp/mode" value="main"/></td><td>''Main''</td><td>Like presentation, but a tab can claim the //i-am-main// admin role and gate who is allowed to present. Without an admin, falls back to last-wins.</td></tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<% endif %>

! SSE status

|! Field | ! Value |
|SSE active | <$text text={{{ [[$:/status/wikilabs/tw-mcp/sse-server-active]get[text]] :else[[no]] }}}/> |
|Current mode | <$text text=<<mode>>/> |
|Per-tab tiddlers filter | <$text text={{{ [[$:/config/wikilabs/tw-mcp/per-tab-tiddlers]get[text]] :else[[default]] }}}/> |

<% if [<mode>!match[default]] %>

! Presenter

''Current presenter:''<% if [<presenterCid>!is[blank]] %> <% if [<presenterName>!is[blank]] %>"''<<presenterName>>''" <% endif %>(<<presenterCid>>)<% else %> (none)<% endif %><% if [<presenterCid>!is[blank]match<myCid>] %> ''(this tab)''<% endif %>

<<presenterButtons>>

In presentation mode the presenter's `$:/StoryList` and other per-tab tiddlers broadcast to all other tabs. Last-claim-wins. Closing the presenter's browser releases the role.

<% if [<mode>match[main]] %>

! Main (admin)

''Current main:''<% if [<mainCid>!is[blank]] %> <% if [<mainName>!is[blank]] %>"''<<mainName>>''" <% endif %>(<<mainCid>>)<% else %> (none)<% endif %><% if [<mainCid>!is[blank]match<myCid>] %> ''(this tab)''<% endif %>

<% if [<mainCid>is[blank]] %><$button>
<$action-sendmessage $message="tm-mcp-claim-main"/>
<$action-sendmessage $message="tm-mcp-refresh-clients"/>
Become Main
</$button> <% endif %><% if [<mainCid>!is[blank]match<myCid>] %><$button message="tm-mcp-release-main">Release Main</$button><% endif %>

When an admin is set, the admin alone can change SSE settings (mode, per-tab filter) and grant presenter status. Without an admin, main mode falls back to last-wins, like presentation.

<% if [<mainCid>!is[blank]match<myCid>] %>

!! Connected clients

<$button message="tm-mcp-refresh-clients">Refresh client list</$button>

<$list filter="[list[$:/state/wikilabs/tw-mcp/clients-list!!list]]" variable="cid" emptyMessage="(no clients seen yet -- click Refresh)">
<$let
	usernameField={{{ [[username-]addsuffix<cid>] }}}
	uname={{{ [[$:/state/wikilabs/tw-mcp/clients-list]get<usernameField>] }}}
>

* <% if [<uname>!is[blank]] %>"''<<uname>>''" <% endif %>(<<cid>>)<% if [<cid>match<presenterCid>] %> ''(presenter)''<% endif %><% if [<cid>match<myCid>] %> ''(this tab)''<% endif %><% if [<cid>!match<presenterCid>] %> <$button message="tm-mcp-grant-presenter" param=<<cid>>>Grant presenter</$button><% endif %>
</$let>
</$list>

<% endif %>

<% endif %>

<% endif %>

! Per-tab tiddlers

<% if [<locked>match[yes]] %>//Locked: only the admin can edit `$:/config/wikilabs/tw-mcp/per-tab-tiddlers` while main mode is active.//<% else %>Edit `$:/config/wikilabs/tw-mcp/per-tab-tiddlers` to extend or override which titles are treated as per-tab view state.<% endif %> The value is a TW filter; default:

```
[[$:/StoryList]] [[$:/HistoryList]] [prefix[$:/state/]]
```

Changes take effect on the next wiki change without restart.

</$let>
